answers.body_markdown:
You could do an if statement in template tied to your settings.py Debug variable value and pass that value from your view. 

**Your View**

```
from .settings import DEBUG
def your_view(request):
    context={‘debug_var’: DEBUG}
    return render (request, “template.html”,context )
```


**Your Template**
```
{% if debug_value %}

{% debug %}

{% else %}
&lt;p&gt;No debug &lt;/p&gt;

{% endif %}
```

